# List of acts of the 2nd session of the 2nd Parliament of the United Kingdom

This is a complete list of acts of the 2nd session of the 2nd Parliament of the United Kingdom which had regnal year  44 Geo. 3. This session met from  met from 22 November 1803 until 31 July 1804.
